08/23/81	note.compin

Syntax:  .ifi note


Function:
This macro formats an "inline" note in the text.


Macro action:
1) inserts appropriate paragraph separation space.
2) temporarily increases the left margin indentation by three indenta-
   tion levels.
3) Places "Note:" in Century Schoolbook Bold Roman, hanging by two
   indentation levels on the first line of the note.


NOTES:
1) A use of this macro must be followed immediately by the text of the
   note.
2) Use of any of the several paragraph macros at the end of the note
   text reverts the temporary left indentation.
